# PantheonOS Community License v1.0

PantheonOS Community Edition (CE) is free for:

- Personal use  
- Research  
- Education  
- Non-profit experimentation  
- Academic papers  
- Local single-user deployments  
- Community forks (non-commercial)

PantheonOS CE is NOT free for:

- Organizational use
- SaaS applications
- Cloud orchestration platforms
- Enterprise workflows
- Multi-user deployments
- Commercial products

For commercial use, an Enterprise License is required.